        public final String getIndicator()
        Description copied from interface: PrologIndicator
        Gets the term indicator represented by one string with the format functor/arity. More formally the indicator string is formed by the concatenation of PrologIndicator.getFunctor() and PrologIndicator.getArity() separated by slash.
